{"tid":1719321,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"11.16同志遊行將更改為集會活動","createTime":"2019-11-14T05:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:13:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"41e97db9db3dd36fa51ccfe5caa0fbaed6dfaabf","tid":1719321,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"香港同志遊行2019將更改為集會活動。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港警方發出之不反對通知書，香港同志遊行2019活動只獲批准以集會型式進行，因此2019年11月16日的同志遊行將會改為集會。<br />\n<br />\n大會將以原定終點作為是次集會地點（中環愛丁堡廣場，時間：下午2時至6時），原定的節目及攤位安排亦會就是次更改而作出調整，如造成您的不便，敬請原諒。<br />\n<br />\n各位希望參與11月16日香港同志遊行（集會）的朋友們，請留意本籌委會公佈的消息。<br />\nFacebook專頁：<a href=\"http://fb.com/hkpride\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fhkpride&d=7CNMK8%2FfTiCK2iXV1c%2BwrARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=305c1373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/hkpride</a><br />\nTelegram Channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/hkpride\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkpride&d=7CNMK8%2FfTiCK2iXV1c%2BwrARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=0aaea18c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkpride</a><br />\n<br />\n[#hkp2019] 14/11/2019 Announcement<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong Pride Parade 2019 will change to a public meeting.<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong Police have issued a Letter of No Objection to the public event held by the Hong Kong Pride Parade only in the form of a public meeting on November 16, 2019.<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong Pride Parade committee have decided to hold the public meeting at the original end point of the parade (Edinburgh Place) from 2 pm to 6 pm. We apologize for the inconvenience caused to the changes for the scheduled performances and booths.<br />\n<br />\nFor those joining our Hong Kong Pride Parade Public Meeting this Saturday on November 16, please follow our Facebook and Telegram Channel for the updated news about our event!<br />\n<br />\nWe hope all of you who are either helping or joining this year&rsquo;s Pride Parade(Assembly), please stay tune with our page and channel for the latest information.<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"http://fb.com/hkpride\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fhkpride&d=7CNMK8%2FfTiCK2iXV1c%2BwrARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=305c1373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/hkpride</a><br />\nTelegram Channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/hkpride\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkpride&d=7CNMK8%2FfTiCK2iXV1c%2BwrARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=0aaea18c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkpride</a>"},{"pid":"8bf1aac295608071300c2e61b39b280385ea3ea4","tid":1719321,"uid":56223,"like":3,"dislike":29,"score":-26,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:21:06.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解呢個時候搞個同志集會<br />\n我係唔會出<br />\n<br />\n利申：黃但反同"},{"pid":"4ea5284028e70e6c36e7f98871c2f925173740c5","tid":1719321,"uid":263038,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"8bf1aac295608071300c2e61b39b280385ea3ea4","tid":1719321,"uid":56223,"like":3,"dislike":29,"score":-26,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:21:06.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解呢個時候搞個同志集會<br />\n我係唔會出<br />\n<br />\n利申：黃但反同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:25:08.000Z","msg":"年年都有<br />\n搞咗好多年㗎啦<br />\n年年都係呢個時間"},{"pid":"eacddd8fb986fb673b9ce1e1d257fa221e1508f4","tid":1719321,"uid":278530,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"8bf1aac295608071300c2e61b39b280385ea3ea4","tid":1719321,"uid":56223,"like":3,"dislike":29,"score":-26,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:21:06.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解呢個時候搞個同志集會<br />\n我係唔會出<br />\n<br />\n利申：黃但反同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:27:49.000Z","msg":"每年都有㗎喎<br />\n呢個日期宣傳咗好耐<br />\n<br />\n真深黃是不應反同的<br />\n原因自己諗"},{"pid":"047700d767eb7b3120f8cb37979c795dcde5b614","tid":1719321,"uid":332860,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"8bf1aac295608071300c2e61b39b280385ea3ea4","tid":1719321,"uid":56223,"like":3,"dislike":29,"score":-26,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:21:06.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解呢個時候搞個同志集